### 6. 日志可能泄露敏感信息

**位置**: 所有使用 logger 的地方

**风险**: 日志可能包含 API Token、用户数据等敏感信息

**修复建议**:

```typescript
// ✅ 创建日志过滤器
const sensitiveKeys = [
  'password',
  'token',
  'apiKey',
  'secret',
  'authorization',
  'cookie',
  'session'
];

function sanitizeLogData(data: any): any {
  if (typeof data === 'string') {
    return data.replace(/Bearer\s+[A-Za-z0-9\-._~+/]+=*/g, 'Bearer ***');
  }

  if (typeof data !== 'object' || data === null) {
    return data;
  }

  const sanitized = { ...data };

  for (const key of Object.keys(sanitized)) {
    const lowerKey = key.toLowerCase();

    if (sensitiveKeys.some(sk => lowerKey.includes(sk))) {
      sanitized[key] = '***';
    } else if (typeof sanitized[key] === 'object') {
      sanitized[key] = sanitizeLogData(sanitized[key]);
    }
  }

  return sanitized;
}

// 使用
logger.info({ 
  user: sanitizeLogData(userData),
  request: sanitizeLogData(req.body) 
}, 'User login');
```

